OL,3,CEast Midlands Ambulance service faced
OL,4,Cdelays of 18,000 hours in February
OL,6,FEast Midlands Ambulance Service,
OL,7,Fserving Nottinghamshire, Derbyshire,
OL,8,FLeicestershire, Rutland, Lincolnshire,
OL,9,Fand Northamptonshire, says it faced
OL,10,F"significant operational hurdles" last
OL,11,Fmonth, with delays averaging 628 hours
OL,12,Fper day across the region.JDuring a
OL,13,Fboard meeting on Tuesday 5 March, Ben
OL,14,FHoldaway, EMAS's Director of
OL,15,FOperations, voiced concern over the
OL,16,Fimpact of these delays on both staff
OL,17,Fmorale and the ambulance service's
OL,18,Fefficiency.
