OL,3,CEast Midlands Ambulance service faced
OL,4,Cdelays of 18,000 hours in February
OL,6,FHe identified the Queen's Medical
OL,7,FCentre, operated by Nottingham
OL,8,FUniversity Hospitals (NUH), as a key
OL,9,Fcontributor to the problem,
OL,10,Fresponsible for 28% of the lost hours.
OL,11,FThey say the crux of the issue lies in
OL,12,Fthe lack of available hospital beds,
OL,13,Fforcing ambulances to wait longer to
OL,14,Fhand over patients.
