OL,6,FMr Holdaway said: "What compounds the
OL,7,F18,000 lost hours is that 28% of those
OL,8,Fwere lost at NUH, our busiest
OL,9,Fhospital, and 18 per cent at Leicester
OL,10,FRoyal Infirmary, our second busiest.
OL,12,F"46% of our hours were lost in those
OL,13,Fhospitals which adds pressure
OL,14,Felsewhere as we have to move resources
OL,15,Faround.
OL,26,@nD@SOUtD@AOU
