OL,6,F"We have been working to highlight the
OL,7,Frisk we are facing through NUH, not
OL,8,Fjust through lost hours but also the
OL,9,Fmoral injuries through staff having to
OL,10,Fcohort patients and waiting with
OL,11,Fpatients for a long period of time.
OL,13,F"We've been raising these concerns
OL,14,Fwith the Integrated Care Board (ICB)
OL,15,Fand hospital. Lots of escalation
OL,16,Fmeetings are taking place until we are
OL,17,Fmore assured we will see improvement."
