OL,6,FMr Henderson told the meeting: "I am
OL,7,Fconfident we will see further change
OL,8,Fand improvement but it would be wrong
OL,9,Fto say the improvements have been
OL,10,Fsustained.
OL,12,F"It would be unfair to say the
OL,13,Fmeetings aren't having any impact.
OL,14,FThis is not just a hospital issue.
OL,16,F"It is clear to say, we would deliver
OL,17,Fall the trajectories if the handover
OL,18,Fdelays weren't present.
