OL,4,Cdelays of 18,000 hours in February
OL,6,F"That's not to say we haven't got our
OL,7,Fown internal inefficiencies but there
OL,8,Fis a clear correlation between
OL,9,Fhandover delays and our inability to
OL,10,Frespond.
OL,12,F"That scrutiny of handover is well and
OL,13,Ftruly understood, addressing it is a
OL,14,Fdifferent challenge as it is deep-
OL,15,Frooted.
OL,17,F"Almost 50 per cent of our lost hours
OL,18,Fare being experienced by our biggest
OL,19,Facutes (hospitals) in the region. That
OL,20,Fhas a profound impact.
