OL,6,FShe said: "If somebody is that ill,
OL,7,Fthey should not be returned to the
OL,8,Fambulance. From a patient perspective
OL,9,Fit is abysmal.
OL,11,F"For the paramedics, it is not part of
OL,12,Fwhat they came into the job to do.
OL,14,F"That worries me more than a lot of
OL,15,Fother stuff. It's not acceptable and
OL,16,Fwe need to keep a tight focus on it."
