OL,6,FDr Keith Girling, Medical Director at
OL,7,FNottingham University Hospitals NHS
OL,8,FTrust, said: "We apologise to those
OL,9,Fpatients who have experienced long
OL,10,Fwaits. We are working closely with
OL,11,FEast Midlands Ambulance Service and
OL,12,Fother system partners to improve flow
OL,13,Fthrough the hospital and transfer
OL,14,Fpatients into the care of our
OL,15,Femergency department as quickly as
OL,16,Fpossible.
